<ul class="project-title-and-text">

    <li class="project-title">
        Slap
    </li>

    <li class="project-type">
        Product / Packaging Design
    </li>

    <li class="project-tools">
        Photoshop, Illustrator, Figma
    </li>

    <li class="project-objective-title">
        Objective
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        To create a package and product design for a canned drink.
    </li>

    <li class="project-process-title">
        About
    </li>

    <li class="project-body-text">
        "Slap" is a citrus-flavored energy drink. This project is a 4-pack that contains
        four different flavors: lemon, key lime, mandarin, and grapefruit. The name "Slap" is attributed
        to the bite of sourness from citrus fruits that is akin to getting slapped in the face. The die line
        of the package is a single sheet, making it easy for assembly and for commercial shipping in large amounts.
    </li>

    <!-- <li class="project-process-title">
